description: This chicken stir-fry is a great option for a midweek meal. It’s ready in just 25 minutes and features crunchy, green broccolini.
keywords: Stir-fry,Low saturated fat,Seafood free,Tree nut free,Egg free,Low sugar,Sesame free,Broccolini,High protein,Chicken,Low fat,Dairy free
name: Campbell’s Chicken & Broccolini Stir-fry Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 0.5 bunch green spring onions, sliced thinly

recipeInstructions.text: Heat the oil in a wok or large frying pan over high heat. Add half the chicken and cook for 2-3 minutes until golden. Repeat with remaining chicken add garlic and cook for 1 minute. Transfer to a bowl. Combine Campbell’s Real Stock Chicken, soy sauce and cornflour in a jug, stir well to combine.
Add broccolini to the pan. Cook for 1 min. Pour in stock mixture and bring to the boil. Stir until the liquid starts to thicken. Return cooked chicken and stir through until combined.
Stir through green spring onion and serve with steamed rice.
